"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋個麵都食唔飽，真係八方雲集都好過佢，仲要唔平<br />\n<br />\n睇完杜汶澤食，我比條link個fd睇笑鳩佢淒涼，連個兩條女都覺得唔掂先叫呀澤試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749e3b0a06ba470e67bd9992c6640f8de98dd035","tid":299440,"uid":74640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"我食個2種水餃真心唔錯<br />\n但煎餃睇黎係伏好在無試"},{"pid":"0312c2827b31815d1ae313b6ba3580445f575b85","tid":299440,"uid":12536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"呢間野屯門分店伏到<br />\n米線個湯底好似清水咁無味<br />\n仲要叫乜無乜<br />\n成餐飯得芝士煎餃ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞絲粉皮啲粉皮好似未熟咁 un到<br />\n見到佢係荃灣開分店即刻屌左聲<br />\n<br />\n去荃灣我會食荃昌間餃子屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d36ebbfbf124f5b59189bf3ee51c0c579834cc","tid":299440,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"60蚊一碗面一個小食咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b7e5f4572789442b63b59b7f5a349c25557cf3","tid":299440,"uid":14130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"認真，又貴又唔好食"}]}